@article{ISI:000478005700030,
	Abstract = {{With the development and application of advanced technologies such as
   Cyber Physical System, Internet of Things, Industrial Internet of
   Things, Artificial Intelligence, Big Data, Cloud Computing, Blockchain,
   etc., more manufacturing enterprises are transforming to intelligent
   enterprises. Smart manufacturing systems (SMSs) have become the focus of
   attention of some countries and manufacturing enterprises. At present,
   there are some applications of SMSs in different industrial fields.
