@article{ISI:000455619900020,
	Abstract = {{Industry 4.0 is expected to deliver significant gains in productivity by
   assimilating several technological advancements including cloud
   computing, the Internet-of-Things, and smart devices. However, it is
   unclear how these technologies should be leveraged together to deliver
   the promised benefits. We present the architecture design of an
   information system that integrates these technologies to support hybrid
