   assets into services. As cloud becomes the basis of most innovative
   manufacturing IT systems, its future role in Cyber-physical Production
   Systems has to be properly investigated, as their interoperability will
   play a role of vital importance. In this paper, after a brief
   introduction to cloud criticality and cloud-based manufacturing, the
